        Musician's Canvas v<VERSION>
             <OS> version
This is a multi-track music recording
application (DAW) for desktop PCs. Features
include recording from any audio input,
recording MIDI tracks, on-screen virtual
MIDI keybaord, audio effects & amp
simulation, & mixing all tracks to a single
audio file. Supports FLAC & WAV audio file
formats. This is free software & is designed
to be easy to use.
